Death Academy



A school assignment on serial killers gets an unexpected turn when one of the students make contact with a previously convicted murderer. The killer, who has just recently completed his sentence, explain to the students that he is innocent and he knows who the real killer is. The students become so convinced of his story that they decide to break into the school at night to try to find evidence against the real killer. But someone has become aware of their plans, someone who is willing to go to any length to keep his secrets. When the students have managed to break into the school, they quickly realize that they are stuck in a death trap... along with a psychopathic mass murderer.

